00:20:17.830 --> 00:20:20.920 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes we don't look after
the most important asset

00:20:20.920 --> 00:20:22.990 align:middle line:84%
of achieving that goal,
which is ourselves.

00:20:22.990 --> 00:20:26.620 align:middle line:84%
How do you bring sort of
self-care and even self-love,

00:20:26.620 --> 00:20:28.930 align:middle line:84%
I would say, because a lot
of us beat ourselves up

00:20:28.930 --> 00:20:30.310 align:middle line:90%
with our own internal voice.

00:20:30.310 --> 00:20:32.360 align:middle line:84%
