wanted to do in my life,

00:22:45.270 --> 00:22:46.070 align:middle line:90%
what would that be?

00:22:46.070 --> 00:22:48.190 align:middle line:84%
And I feel like that is
the biggest self-care

00:22:48.190 --> 00:22:50.310 align:middle line:90%
